    {
      "id": "insight:b48adb2454ae4000",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "I'm with Sophie Laurent, enduro racer and coach.",
        "insight_type": "unknown",
        "position_hint": 0.5
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:ddd65689a99a0f26",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Today's episode is sponsored by Strava.",
        "insight_type": "unknown",
        "position_hint": 0.5
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-01",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Maya"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:6c9d9f4e18265591",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 118,
        "char_start": 6,
        "episode_id": "4a626fea-ed45-5ce0-a5c1-4e39d22beaad",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Welcome back to Singletrack Sessions. I'm with Sophie Laurent, enduro racer and coach. Sophie, good to have you.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 6000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 0,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-02",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Sophie Laurent"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:e2817293d2bb29a6",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 175,
        "char_start": 135,
        "episode_id": "4a626fea-ed45-5ce0-a5c1-4e39d22beaad",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Maya. Always happy to talk shop.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:1acdc19b9d1bd255",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 276,
        "char_start": 182,
        "episode_id": "4a626fea-ed45-5ce0-a5c1-4e39d22beaad",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Today's episode is sponsored by Strava. Strava is the home for athletes. Try strava.com today.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:f2d6d8372065fd66",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 336,
        "char_start": 276,
        "episode_id": "4a626fea-ed45-5ce0-a5c1-4e39d22beaad",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "People think racing is about nerve. You say it's about risk.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d5240ddf7ed0dba5",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 560,
        "char_start": 353,
        "episode_id": "4a626fea-ed45-5ce0-a5c1-4e39d22beaad",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "It's risk management, honestly. The crash that ends your season is almost never the scary-looking one — it's the boring risk you didn't name. Name the risk before it names you, and half the danger goes away.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:c81152ac90f31fbf",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 777,
        "char_start": 560,
        "episode_id": "4a626fea-ed45-5ce0-a5c1-4e39d22beaad",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "And you have to ride the whole run as a system, not a list of corners. The mistakes come from how one section sets up the next. When I logged a full season of my own crashes, the causes were always two turns upstream.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 36000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 30000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    }
  ],
